	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_ARTY_RAILGUN">
			<Text>Railgun Artillery</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_ARTY_RAILGUN_HELP">
			<Text>Use Railgun Artillery to destroy enemy cities and units. Requires [ICON_RES_URANIUM] Uranium.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_ARTY_RAILGUN_STRATEGY">
			<Text>Railgun Artillery is an upgrade to the Laser Artillery unit. Employing a radically different launch system, this unit can streams of plasma energy, almost without any need of preparation; thus it does not need to set up before firing. It also has much greater ranged strength, making it very dangerous for modern infantry and other land or naval units.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_ARTY_RAILGUN_PEDIA">
			<Text>
				Railgun Artillery is a specialized siege unit, with enhanced capabilities to engage enemy targets up to 4 tiles away. It is available on the discovery of Nuclear Fusion, and does not become obsolete. Requires [ICON_RES_URANIUM] Uranium.
			</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>	
	
